Label: Opening Inventory
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table        INVOP

Label: Crude Oil Light
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table       ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID=OIL,   Oil Density between 0 and 849.999999

Label: Crude Oil Medium
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table       ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID=OIL,   Oil Density between 850 and 899.999999

Label: Crude Oil Heavy
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table       ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID=OIL,   Oil Density between 900 and 924.999999

Label: Crude Oil Ultra Heavy
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table       ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID=OIL,   Oil Density >= 925

Label: Total Crude Oil Production
Value: CALCULATED:  SUM of Conventional Oil Production

Label: Condensate Production
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table       ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID= COND

Label: In Situ Production
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID=OIL,  DEPOSIT_ID not null

Label: Mined Production
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID=CRUDEBIT

Label: Sent for Further Processing
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=FURPROC,  FLUID=CRUDEBIT    (set as negative)

Label: Non-Upgraded Total
Value: CALCULATED:  SUM of Non-Upgraded Production

Label: Upgraded Production
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=PROD,  FLUID= SYNCRD        SUBTRACT      ACTIVITY = FURPROC,   FLUID= SYNCRD

Label: Total Oil Sands Production
Value: CALCULATED:  SUM of Non-Upgraded Production Total and Upgraded Production

Label: Total Production
Value: CALCULATED:  SUM of Total Conventional Oil Production   and   Condensate Production   and    Total Oil Sands Production

Label: Pentanes Plus  - Plant/Gathering Process
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       PROC

Label: Pentanes Plus  - Fractionation Yield
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       FRAC

Label: Skim Oil Recovered
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       Sum of skim oil recovered at Injection Facilities (ABIF)        invop_oil + rec_oil - disp_oil - invcl_oil + invadj_oil

Label: Waste Plant Receipts
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=REC,  Source= ABWP

Label: Other Alberta Receipts
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=ABOT or ABMC, ACTIVITY=REC, Dest=AB_Facility

Label: Butanes reported as Crude Oil or Equivalent
Top Level: Butanes reported as Crude Oil or Equivalent
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       Sum of all facilities:   C4 supply - C4 disposition

Label: NGL reported as Crude Oil or Equivalent
Top Level: NGL reported as Crude Oil or Equivalent
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       Sum of all facilities:   NGL supply - NGL disposition

Label: Pentanes Plus
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=^AB, ACTIVITY=REC, Dest=AB_Facility, FLUID=IC5-SP,NC5-SP,C5-SP,C6-SP

Label: Condensates
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=^AB, ACTIVITY=REC, Dest=AB_Facility, FLUID=COND

Label: Oil
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=^AB, ACTIVITY=REC, Dest=AB_Facility, FLUID=OIL, CRUDEBIT

Label: Synthetic Crude Oil
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=^AB, ACTIVITY=REC, Dest=AB_Facility, FLUID=SYNCRD

Label: Total Imports
Value: CALCULATED:  SUM of Receipts

Label: Flare or Waste
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       FLARWAST

Label: Shrinkage
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       SHR

Label: Closing Inventory
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       INVCL

Label: TOTAL OIL & EQUIVALENT SUPPLY
Value: CALCULATED --  Opening Inventory  PLUS   Total Production     PLUS   Total Receipts   SUBTRACT   Flare or Waste   SUBTRACT  Fuel   SUBTRACT   Shrinkage   SUBTRACT  Closing Inventory  PLUS   Adjustments

Label: Alberta Injection and well use
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      INJ      PLUS       ACTIVITY=DISP, Dest=Well

Label: Alberta Refinery Sales
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=ABRF, ACTIVITY=DISP, Dest=ABOT or ABMC

Label: Waste Plant Use
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=DISP, Dest=ABWP

Label: Plant Use
Value: FROM Volumetric Summary Activity Table       PLTUSE

Label: Line Fill
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=DISP, Dest=ABLF

Label: Load Fluid
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      LDINVOP - LDINJ  +  LDREC  -  LDINVCL   +   LDINVADJ

Label: Alberta Other Sales
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      Source=AB_Facility and <> ABRF, ACTIVITY=DISP, Dest=ABOT or ABMC

Label: Total Alberta Use
Value: CALCULATED:  SUM of Alberta Use

Label: Removals from Alberta
Value: FROM Volumetric Reporting Activity Table      ACTIVITY=DISP   AND   Dest<>AB    OR     Dest='NEB pipeline'   OR  Dest='ABRC'
